data.description: Welcome to The Country Club of Mount Dora, a premier golf community. This exquisite home is a true gem for those seeking luxury, comfort, and breathtaking views of the golf course and pond. The open floor plan invites you to explore the spacious 2062 square feet of living area, where each space is thoughtfully designed for both relaxation and entertainment. This home has high ceilings and an abundance of natural light throughout the home. Plantation shutters, tile and engineered hardwood flooring add to the luxurious feel of this home. The beautifully integrated kitchen and family room provide the perfect setting for effortless entertainment. Whether you're preparing culinary delights in the well-appointed kitchen or enjoying the company of friends and family in the spacious family room, the flow of this space ensures everyone is part of the festivities.   The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom with a separate shower and a luxurious garden tub. You'll also find a spacious walk-in closet, offering ample storage space for your clothing and personal belongings.  In addition to the three bedrooms, there is an office with French doors, allowing you to focus on tasks while working from the comfort of your home. Or use this versatile space as a craft, game or tv room.   You can experience the panoramic views of the golf course and serene pond from all the living areas, the primary suite and the screened lanai.   For your peace of mind and comfort, this home comes with a new roof and a new air conditioning system installed in 2022. To maximize easy living, lawncare is provided for $85.00 per month.   The Country Club of Mount Dora is more than just a community; it's a lifestyle. With its premier golf facilities, beautiful surroundings, and convenient location, this is a place where you can truly live your best life. Golf, pickleball, tennis, pool and member dinners and events are offered with membership to The Country Club of Mount Dora. The community is located just minutes away from historic downtown Mount Dora-filled with charming shops, restaurants, and lake front activities. Enjoy the ease and charm of small-town living combined with the convenient proximity to Orlando. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home. Schedule a viewing and experience the The Country Club of Mount Dora lifestyle today.
